org.webcurator.domain.model.core
Class Profile

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.core.Profile
All Implemented Interfaces:
AgencyOwnable
public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
implements AgencyOwnable

The Profile object contains information that enables the user to control how a profile takes place. This class is tied quite directly to the Heritrix XML based profiles.

Author:
bbeaumont
